s-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x28BB9;</span></a><a href="/whv/𥖾"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x255BE;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤢼"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x248BC;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤑦"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x24466;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤁷"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x24077;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡣪"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x218EA;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡂓"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x21093;</span></a><a href="/whv/𠐝"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2041D;</span></a><a href="/whv/讁"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8B81;</span></a><a href="/whv/瓋"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x74CB;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
